channel.description:
[center]AnarchyScape started in February this year by me, Evan. I've been coding it off and on and have done a lot of stuff to the source. I'm open for suggestions on what to add in the near future. I hope to start a great community with this server and hopefully finish my goals.
-Evan
Client download: http://dl.dropbox.com/u/54825351/client.jar
Features: -New level up 99 get cash! -Vote4Cash -Custom Construction -GWD -Flawless switching -508 Maps -Dicing -New items -Money pouch fully working -No Dupes -Godswords,Dclaws,Korasi fully working -All Nex armours -Loyalty titles -Donator points -Fair EXP rate -634 Items -Lots of fun!
Npcs: -Bork -GWD Bosses -Corp -Jad -All Strykewyms -Dagannoth Kings -Barrows
Items: -New Torva -Pernix -Virtus -Max Cape -New Bandos -Completionist Cape -Tokhaar-kal -Chaotics -Spirit Shields -Working Ring of Vigour -Vesta -Statius -Steadfast, Ragefire, Glaiven Boots
Pictures: PKP Shop [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/294ky02.png[/img]
Switches(Low quality video, server has better graphics) http://gifninja.com/animated-gifs/283107/switches

Spec weapons(Many more) [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/2vx3z1k.png[/img]
Will upload more pictures later on[/center]
